    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition vehicle that presents beautifully throughout and should strongly appeal to a buyer looking for a top-tier example. The paint, body, and overall finish show excellent care, with a clean, highly polished appearance and no notable cosmetic issues standing out. The interior is equally impressive, appearing very well preserved with minimal visible wear, and the car gives the impression of careful ownership rather than heavy use. This is the kind of vehicle a discerning buyer can feel good about showing, enjoying, and owning with confidence.",
