    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward value over cosmetics, but it remains a practical option for commuting, light errands, or as a project. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong value for the right buyer.",
