    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and could be a great fit for someone who wants basic transportation or a project to tinker with. A solid opportunity to get into a car without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and worth a look if you\u2019re practical and know how to spot value.",
