    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid driver-project with a tough stance and plenty of usable life left. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still presents as a complete, honest machine with a drivetrain that feels eager and mechanically straightforward to sort and maintain. Ideal for someone wanting an affordable entry point, commuter beater, or weekend wrenching platform. If you appreciate a car with character and practical upside, this one has the bones to be a rewarding buy.",
      "price": 5950.0,
