    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A diamond in the rough with unmistakable character, this car has the kind of presence that turns a simple drive into a story. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates personality over perfection\u2014whether you\u2019re looking for an affordable runaround, a hands-on project, or a vehicle with a little soul left to give. There\u2019s honest wear that speaks to a life well-lived, but that same patina gives it a rugged, lived-in charm you just can\u2019t fake. Priced to move and full of potential for the right buyer.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
