    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced with its age and wear in mind, and for the money, it\u2019s a great chance to get into a car without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really solid buy.",
